00:15:39.780 --> 00:15:43.380
So we can see what happened in response to that.

00:15:43.380 --> 00:15:45.900
First of all, we have these two actions from Mirai.

00:15:45.900 --> 00:15:50.900
These are just daemons, so these are the background processes starting up.

